---
description: Shared React components and styles
globs: src/components/**/*.{tsx,scss}
alwaysApply: false
---

# Components

- Use functional components and existing imports (`Layout`, `Seo`, `Link` from `gatsby`).
- Styling: Tailwind utility classes; component SCSS only in `layout.scss`.
- `nav-menu.tsx`: menu order comes from GraphQL + `nav-menu.md`—do not hardcode link lists in the component.
- Avoid adding dependencies for small UI changes.
